&lt;p&gt;Here is my collection of various pieces of advice on academic career issues in mathematics, roughly arranged by the stage of career at which the advice is most pertinent (though of course some of the advice pertains to multiple stages).&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>AI辅助编码时代下的新型生产力与职业发展 | 吴恩达</title><link>https://linguista.cn/static/andrew_ng_ai_coding_career_advices_stanford_2025/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Oct 2025 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/static/andrew_ng_ai_coding_career_advices_stanford_2025/</guid><description>吴恩达在斯坦福CS230课程中指出，AI辅助编码工具已彻底改变开发模式。他强调区分“快速原型开发”与“生产级开发”，并提倡利用AI降低试错成本。文章还探讨了开发者角色的转变，即从编写代码转向审查与架构设计，以及AI时代对技能差距的深远影响。</description></item><item><title>Escape Competition Through Authenticity</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/escape-competition-through-authenticity/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2019 10:35:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/escape-competition-through-authenticity/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/escape-competition-through-authenticity.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
